        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>
            <div class="about-content">
                <p>Jijal Pickles is a family-owned business dedicated to preserving the rich culinary heritage of Pakistan through our authentic, homemade pickles. Our journey began generations ago in the heart of rural Sindh, where traditional recipes were passed down through the family.</p>
                <p>We specialize in creating pickles using age-old techniques combined with modern hygiene standards. Each jar is handcrafted with care, using only the freshest locally sourced ingredients and no artificial preservatives. Our pickles are a perfect blend of traditional flavors and uncompromising quality.</p>
                <p>At Jijal Pickles, we believe in preserving not just vegetables and fruits, but also the cultural heritage and family traditions that make Pakistani cuisine so special. Our commitment to quality ensures that every bite takes you on a journey through the authentic flavors of Pakistan.</p>
            </div>
